      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This AP2-generation example is a masterclass in mechanical harmony. It features the high-revving F22C1 inline-four, utilizing FRM cylinder liners and a forged rotating assembly for peak volumetric efficiency. The longitudinal six-speed manual transmission offers short-throw precision, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory-equipped Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its original X-bone frame rigidity and factory-spec double-wishbone suspension geometry. Every body panel retains its original VIN tag, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation, reflecting a life of meticulous climate-controlled storage. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
